<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 04:10:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列计划征召的极端正统人士远远不能满足军队当前的需求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-planned-draft-of-ultra-orthodox-falls-far-short-of-the-armys-current-needs/00000190-9e56-d41c-abfc-def65b770000</link><description>根据正在制定的计划，两年内将招募约 9,600 名年轻的正统派男子——远少于 63,000 名处于征兵年龄的极端正统男子。只要加沙战争持续下去，总参谋部将继续依靠预备役军人，而且在未来几年边境预计紧张的时期也是如此</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-planned-draft-of-ultra-orthodox-falls-far-short-of-the-armys-current-needs/00000190-9e56-d41c-abfc-def65b770000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，随着卡塔尔休战谈判即将恢复，哈马斯可能在“几天内”达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-hamas-deal-possible-within-days-as-qatar-truce-talks-set-to-resume/00000190-9ef8-dfb2-a799-befd66de0000</link><description>国防部长约夫·加兰特：“现在实现我们的道德义务并将人质带回家的机会有限”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-hamas-deal-possible-within-days-as-qatar-truce-talks-set-to-resume/00000190-9ef8-dfb2-a799-befd66de0000</guid></item><item><title>随着双方前往卡塔尔进行进一步谈判，美国对加沙停火持“谨慎乐观”态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article-live/u-s-cautiously-optimistic-about-gaza-cease-fire-as-sides-head-to-qatar-for-talks/00000190-9fa1-dfb2-a799-bff5e84c0000</link><description>拜登政府将很快向以色列转移延迟炸弹，重型炮弹仍在搁置 ■ 国防部长加兰特：以色列人质交易“窗口有限”，风险可以克服 ■ 纳斯鲁拉：如果以色列和哈马斯达成加沙休战，黎巴嫩战斗将立即停止■ 以色列国防军表示，他们袭击了突破两国边境缓冲区的叙利亚军队目标 ■ 随着战斗加剧，以色列命令加沙城的所有巴勒斯坦人撤离南部</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article-live/u-s-cautiously-optimistic-about-gaza-cease-fire-as-sides-head-to-qatar-for-talks/00000190-9fa1-dfb2-a799-bff5e84c0000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统派拉比领袖指示学生无视以色列军队征召令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/leading-ultra-orthodox-rabbi-instructs-students-to-ignore-israeli-army-call-up-orders/00000190-9f8d-d962-a3b7-9fbf3f350001</link><description>以色列立陶宛极端正统派领袖拉比多夫·兰多 (Rabbi Dov Lando) 写道，“法院已向托拉世界宣战”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:15:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/leading-ultra-orthodox-rabbi-instructs-students-to-ignore-israeli-army-call-up-orders/00000190-9f8d-d962-a3b7-9fbf3f350001</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方知道在准备极端正统征兵时必须谨慎行事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-knows-it-must-tread-carefully-as-it-prepares-for-the-ultra-orthodox-draft/00000190-9dfb-dbad-adfc-fdfbbc8e0000</link><description>以色列国防军计划征召在职和退学的犹太学院学生，并打算赋予拉比对新兵服役的监督权</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 23:25:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-knows-it-must-tread-carefully-as-it-prepares-for-the-ultra-orthodox-draft/00000190-9dfb-dbad-adfc-fdfbbc8e0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：内塔尼亚胡的局试图更改以色列内阁战时会议纪要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/report-netanyahus-bureau-tried-to-alter-minutes-of-war-time-meetings-of-israeli-cabinet/00000190-9ea1-dfb2-a799-bef5354e0000</link><description>总理的前军事秘书几个月前联系了司法部长，敲响了警钟； PMO：报告完全是谎言</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 22:06:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/report-netanyahus-bureau-tried-to-alter-minutes-of-war-time-meetings-of-israeli-cabinet/00000190-9ea1-dfb2-a799-bef5354e0000</guid></item><item><title>“严厉和麦卡锡主义”：以色列议会提出法案，解雇那些被政府视为“支持恐怖”观点的学者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/knesset-advances-bill-to-fire-academics-for-views-seen-as-supporting-terror-by-govt/00000190-9e04-d03e-a5fd-9fb6744f0000</link><description>该提案允许由教育部长担任主席的高等教育委员会要求解雇，但不支付遣散费。大学校长谴责这一“麦卡锡主义”措施，警告称这可能会煽动针对教师的运动，并可能导致针对教师的暴力行为</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 20:27:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/knesset-advances-bill-to-fire-academics-for-views-seen-as-supporting-terror-by-govt/00000190-9e04-d03e-a5fd-9fb6744f0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么民主党和共和党在以色列和加沙问题上的纲领如此模糊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-10/ty-article/.highlight/why-the-democratic-and-gop-platforms-on-israel-and-gaza-are-so-vague/00000190-9dab-dbad-adfc-fdbbef040000</link><description>在目前尚不清楚拜登的连任竞选活动是否能维持足够的支持度过一周之际，围绕拜登以色列政策的细微差别的任何辩论都无关紧要。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 18:34:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-10/ty-article/.highlight/why-the-democratic-and-gop-platforms-on-israel-and-gaza-are-so-vague/00000190-9dab-dbad-adfc-fdbbef040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列没有赢得加沙战争。它的其他战争也没有那么成功</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-not-won-the-gaza-war-its-other-wars-werent-so-successful-either/00000190-9caf-da1a-adf0-9ebfc5720000</link><description>历史上第二长的战争已经过去九个月了，以色列是否擅长战争是一个令人烦恼的问题，并提出了巨大的问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 17:24:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-not-won-the-gaza-war-its-other-wars-werent-so-successful-either/00000190-9caf-da1a-adf0-9ebfc5720000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡如何系统性地挫败哈马斯释放人质的谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-timeline/.premium/how-netanyahu-has-systematically-foiled-talks-to-release-hostages-from-hamas-captivity/00000190-9b91-d591-a7ff-fff341120000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 17:09:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-timeline/.premium/how-netanyahu-has-systematically-foiled-talks-to-release-hostages-from-hamas-captivity/00000190-9b91-d591-a7ff-fff341120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 278 天：内塔尼亚胡表示，如果不跨越“红线”，他承诺停战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-278-netanyahu-says-committed-to-truce-if-it-doesnt-cross-red-lines/00000190-9d7f-dbad-adfc-fdff54ad0001</link><description>由摩萨德负责人率领的以色列代表团前往卡塔尔参加休战峰会，参与峰会的官员称其为“决定性的”。 ■ 人质家属踏上从耶路撒冷前往特拉维夫的为期三天的游行。 ■ 加沙的报道称，以色列对流离失所者营地的袭击造成 29 人死亡，主要是妇女和儿童 ■ 以色列国防军表示，约有 30 枚火箭从黎巴嫩发射到以色列北部 ■ 战争进入 278 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 16:45:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-278-netanyahu-says-committed-to-truce-if-it-doesnt-cross-red-lines/00000190-9d7f-dbad-adfc-fdff54ad0001</guid></item><item><title>最新的空中情报：真主党在以色列境内的镜头中最可怕的教训</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/up-to-date-aerial-intel-the-scariest-lesson-from-hezbollahs-footage-of-inside-israel/00000190-9cf9-d41c-abfc-defd5de40000</link><description>多架无人机的航拍照片显示，真主党拥有实时的打击情报。发表后，它袭击了戈兰高地的纳法赫基地，造成两名平民死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 16:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/up-to-date-aerial-intel-the-scariest-lesson-from-hezbollahs-footage-of-inside-israel/00000190-9cf9-d41c-abfc-defd5de40000</guid></item><item><title>获救的以色列人质起诉在加沙雇佣巴勒斯坦劫持者的美国非营利组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-sues-u-s-non-profit-that-employed-palestinian-captor-in-gaza/00000190-9c81-d07e-a798-beb136350000</link><description>该诉讼称，该组织的领导人“故意并故意获取和传播哈马斯的宣传”，并“物质上支持”哈马斯的恐怖主义行为</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-sues-u-s-non-profit-that-employed-palestinian-captor-in-gaza/00000190-9c81-d07e-a798-beb136350000</guid></item><item><title>资产还是负债？民主党制定选举纲领，以色列仍是热点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/asset-or-liability-israel-remains-flash-point-as-democrats-draw-up-election-platform/00000190-9c0f-d328-a9d1-9dff2dd00000</link><description>周二的在线听证会上，中东问题上的民主分歧十分明显，亲巴勒斯坦不承诺运动的一名领导人呼吁美国停止对以色列的军事援助</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 14:15:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/asset-or-liability-israel-remains-flash-point-as-democrats-draw-up-election-platform/00000190-9c0f-d328-a9d1-9dff2dd00000</guid></item><item><title>谁说以色列人不能灵活变通？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/who-said-israelis-cant-be-flexible/00000190-97db-d590-affd-b7df48920000</link><description>以色列人将柔术训练（突破精神和身体极限）视为治愈和赋权的源泉</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 14:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/who-said-israelis-cant-be-flexible/00000190-97db-d590-affd-b7df48920000</guid></item><item><title>这些以色列士兵在10月7日受伤。这就是他们现在的生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/going-back-to-israeli-soldiers-wounded-on-october-7-the-trauma-isnt-over/00000190-9c3b-d262-a9f4-dfbf67260000</link><description>《国土报》再次探访了 10 月 7 日受伤的四名以色列士兵，了解他们的艰辛旅程。 “如果我在前三周没有得到支持，我想我今天就不会站在这里”</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 12:09:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/going-back-to-israeli-soldiers-wounded-on-october-7-the-trauma-isnt-over/00000190-9c3b-d262-a9f4-dfbf67260000</guid></item><item><title>随着战斗加剧，以色列命令加沙城的巴勒斯坦人向南撤离至代尔巴拉赫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-calls-on-all-residents-of-gaza-city-to-evacuate-south-to-deir-al-balah/00000190-9bfb-d872-a3b5-fffb929e0000</link><description>据加沙人称，以色列军队加大对加沙城周边社区的攻击力度后，数万人再次流离失所，与战争开始时的情况类似。一位居民告诉《国土报》：“当时还有地方可去，但现在从北到南一切都被摧毁了”</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:15:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-calls-on-all-residents-of-gaza-city-to-evacuate-south-to-deir-al-balah/00000190-9bfb-d872-a3b5-fffb929e0000</guid></item><item><title>参与前哨疏散暴力的以色列定居者步行，警方未提交任何报告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-involved-in-outpost-evacuation-violence-to-walk-as-police-file-no-reports/00000190-9bac-d0d3-a5f3-9bbcd2420000</link><description>五名以色列定居者因涉嫌投掷石块而被捕，另一名以色列定居者因向警察喷洒胡椒粉而被捕，但全部被释放。在安全官员的建议下，总理内塔尼亚胡下令撤离，因为他担心来自前哨的犹太人的恐怖行为可能会将约旦河西岸从战争的次要战线变成主要战线</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 10:34:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-involved-in-outpost-evacuation-violence-to-walk-as-police-file-no-reports/00000190-9bac-d0d3-a5f3-9bbcd2420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙中部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-central-gaza-combat/00000190-9c00-de9b-ad99-fc6e206e0000</link><description>21 岁的塔尔·拉哈特 (Tal Lahat) 来自卡法萨瓦 (Kfar Sava)，身后留下父母和兄弟。他曾在以色列军队精锐的马格兰突击队服役</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 09:47:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-central-gaza-combat/00000190-9c00-de9b-ad99-fc6e206e0000</guid></item><item><title>周二以色列北部火箭袭击事件中，两名以色列父母丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-parents-named-as-two-killed-on-tuesdays-rocket-attack-in-northern-israel/00000190-9bee-dcf3-a7d6-9bfe9be10000</link><description>诺亚和尼尔·巴拉内斯在戈兰高地北部的汽车上被真主党火箭直接击中身亡。他们身后留下了三个年龄分别为 18、15 和 13 岁的孩子</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 09:24:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-parents-named-as-two-killed-on-tuesdays-rocket-attack-in-northern-israel/00000190-9bee-dcf3-a7d6-9bfe9be10000</guid></item></channel></rss>